data.name: eucaim_wizard_tool
data.description: The EUCAIM Wizard tool is based on ARX software which is open-source data de-identification / anonymization software that supports various anonymization techniques. The freely available ARX software has been configured for the specific requirements of the EUCAIM platform taking into account the specific imaging and clinical data characteristics.

evidence: "This repository is for data curators / analysts who want to run re-identification risk analysis and utility evaluation in the ARX Data Anonymization Tool, using the EUCAIM Wizard configuration"
"You do not need to build code from this repo just to use the hierarchies/templates." (indicates distribution as configuration/templates in the repo itself)
"What’s in this repository – hierarchies/ ... examples/ ... docs/" (contents are used directly by researchers within ARX to perform anonymization risk and utility analysis)
